snippet.title: Ratchet & Clank®: Full Frontal Assault Debut Trailer
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/games/ratchet-and-clank/?emcid=or-1s-412983

Ratchet & Clank: Full Frontal Assault delivers a concentrated blast of pure fun to the PlayStation 3 and PS Vita, with online multi-player cross-play!
